title: [COMPLETE] Scheduled Maintenance - Feb 12 2016
body:
Hi all,

Just as a heads up - we'll be disabling ranked at **0430am AEDT (Sydney time) on the 12th Feb** ahead of some planned maintenance.  We don't expect there to be any impact to normal gameplay, but we'll be taking Ranked down as a precaution.  We expect this to take around 3 hours, at which point we'll enable Ranked again.

If there are any updates, I'll post them here!

Cheers
Mindstar

replies.body: There's no chance this would be for Dominion would it?
Can you tell us what this is for? And also are we going to get dynamic queue for normals? or atleast replace blind pick

Hi,

This was related to some of the network infrastructure that we use to connect OCE's League servers to the internet.   Not related to queues or anything like that.   :)

Cheers
Mindstar
Why riot, Why? Wasn't Dominion enough?
